{"tid":506791,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Ps4] FIFA18 PRO CLUB招人","createTime":"2017-12-22T14:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T11:39:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d91d3c676f03de69fffd64104abe4fd2025a6795","tid":506791,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"之前即興把球隊（長駐D1）刪除，暫時重新升上D7，希望招收以下位置：<br />\n<br />\n純防中：幫輕ANY防守時的壓力，主要工作為對手進攻時做到防守的第一屏障，盡力拖慢對方進攻等其他隊友回防幫手搶截；球隊進攻時不要過分積極前進，主要做中場連接工作，盡量保持在中圈附近位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/NewNastyCobra-small.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FNewNastyCobra-small.gif&h=81f41c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左翼：懂得無球時為中間拉空而走位，有球時不盲目狂奔向底線，長傳出波需要有質素，不要求有高的過人能力，懂和中場配合推進就可。需要回防。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://78.media.tumblr.com/2eed019b7bf4ff1702fcbb75956394ca/tumblr_o0ga8pVGjP1rhg8bdo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F2eed019b7bf4ff1702fcbb75956394ca%2Ftumblr_o0ga8pVGjP1rhg8bdo1_400.gif&h=d7063953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍門：需要有一定經驗，不要新手龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懂得彈跳救球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26FmSg5aG1HgwXA08/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26FmSg5aG1HgwXA08%2Fsource.gif&h=f848fbfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隊伍陣式及打法：4231。<br />\n有常駐ANY，主要為中間地面短傳進攻，當然也會長傳，只在適當時機放直線。<br />\n<br />\n全體要求：<br />\n- 尊重隊友，不需要獨食鳩扭個人主義者，需要以球隊利益為先。<br />\n- 多走位幫波，不要只向前衝。希望球員盡量做到護球在腳。<br />\n- 不要瘋狂放直線至死位，適當時懂橫傳及後傳。<br />\n- 禁止瘋狂浪射（即明知射門路線被封卻不傳而射龜者）。<br />\n- 多溝通交流討論，幫助大家進步。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有能力及有意試腳者請留TG，謝謝。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9bd588dddf07d2e680970ed6af8a405d995fd987","tid":506791,"uid":21078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"Tg?"},{"pid":"7be2b9f7b33310c73fa98cbcdb